.modal-dialog
  .dl-modal
    form(name="mc")
      .dl-modal-header
        button(class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true")
          img(ng-src='/img/icons/icon_close.png')
        .head 您有 {{join_teams.length}} 个小队和本次活动相关,请选择一个参加!
      .dl-modal-body.clearfix
        .dl_modal_container
          .dl_row.team_select.clearfix(ng-repeat="team in join_teams" ng-click="selcetJoinTeam($index)")
            .dl_md_2
              img.size_56(ng-src="{{team.logo}}")
            .dl_md_8
              .dl_row
                a(href="/group/home/{{team._id}}" target="_blank")
                  span {{team.name}}
            .dl_md_1(ng-if="team.selected")
              input(type="radio")
      .dl-modal-footer.clearfix
        button.cancel_btn.dl_btn_large(data-dismiss="modal") #{__("CANCEL")}
        button.dl_btn.dl_btn_large(data-dismiss="modal" ng-click="joinCampaign()" ng-disabled="selected_index==-1") 就用这个队参加!